---
---
<div class="footprint">
  <div class="cell">
    <div class="kind">in your process</div>
    <div class="num">&lt;10<span class="unit">MB</span></div>
    <div class="desc">
      The <b>client</b> — thin, synchronous-safe, fire-and-forget. One dependency (<b>msgpack</b>).
      Sits inside your Python service, adds no blocking calls.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cell">
    <div class="kind">one per service, isolated</div>
    <div class="num">~43<span class="unit">MB</span></div>
    <div class="desc">
      An <b>async sidecar</b> spawned alongside your app. Handles Telegram, dedup, rate-limit,
      anomaly detection — in its own process, so a bug in observability never crashes production.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .footprint {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(30, 26, 21, 0.15);
    padding-top: 28px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }
  .cell {
    padding: 4px 24px 6px 24px;
    border-left: 1px solid rgba(30, 26, 21, 0.15);
  }
  .cell:first-child { border-left: none; padding-left: 0; }
  .kind {
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 44px;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-sumi);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .unit {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-left: 6px;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }
  .desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-sumi-soft);
    margin-top: 12px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    max-width: 30em;
  }
  .desc b { color: var(--color-sumi); font-weight: 600; }
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .footprint { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .cell + .cell {
      border-left: none;
      padding-left: 0;
      margin-top: 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(30, 26, 21, 0.15);
      padding-top: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
